msgid "Mangrove"
msgstr "Mangrovia"

msgid "Mangrove Roots"
msgstr "Radici di Mangrovia"

msgid "Mangrove roots are decorative blocks that form as part of mangrove trees."
msgstr ""
"Le radici di mangrovia sono dei blocchi decorativi formati come parte degli "
"alberi di mangrovia."

msgid "Mangrove Propagule"
msgstr ""

msgid "Needs soil and light to grow"
msgstr ""

msgid "When placed on soil (such as dirt) and exposed to light, an propagule will grow into an mangrove after some time."
msgstr ""

msgid "Hanging Propagule"
msgstr ""

msgid "Grows on Mangrove leaves"
msgstr ""

msgid "water logged mangrove roots"
msgstr ""

msgid "Mangrove roots, despite being a full block, can be waterlogged and do not flow water out"
msgstr ""

msgid "These cannot be crafted yet only occure when get in contact of water."
msgstr ""

msgid "Muddy Mangrove Roots"
msgstr ""

msgid "crafted with Mud and Mangrove roots"
msgstr ""

msgid "Muddy Mangrove Roots is a block from mangrove swamp.It drowns player a bit inside it."
msgstr ""
